#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.40:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Nīvaraṇavagga"
msgstr "4. Hindrances"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Nīvaraṇasutta"
msgstr "40. Hindrances"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.40:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, nīvaraṇā andhakaraṇā acakkhukaraṇā aññāṇakaraṇā "
"paññānirodhikā vighātapakkhiyā anibbānasaṃvattanikā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these five hindrances are destroyers of sight, vision, and "
"knowledge. They block wisdom, they’re on the side of anguish, and they don’t "
"lead to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kāmacchandanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave, andhakaraṇaṃ acakkhukaraṇaṃ aññāṇakaraṇaṃ "
"paññānirodhikaṃ vighātapakkhiyaṃ anibbānasaṃvattanikaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Sensual desire, ill will, dullness and drowsiness, restlessness and remorse, "
"and doubt."

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.4"
msgid "Byāpādanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.5"
msgid "thinamiddhanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.6"
msgid "uddhaccakukkuccanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.7"
msgid ""
"vicikicchānīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave, andhakaraṇaṃ acakkhukaraṇaṃ aññāṇakaraṇaṃ "
"paññānirodhikaṃ vighātapakkhiyaṃ anibbānasaṃvattanikaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.8"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca nīvaraṇā andhakaraṇā acakkhukaraṇā aññāṇakaraṇā "
"paññānirodhikā vighātapakkhiyā anibbānasaṃvattanikā."
msgstr ""
"These five hindrances are destroyers of sight, vision, and knowledge. They "
"block wisdom, they’re on the side of anguish, and they don’t lead to "
"extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.98"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.40:2.1"
msgid ""
"Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā cakkhukaraṇā ñāṇakaraṇā paññābuddhiyā "
"avighātapakkhiyā nibbānasaṃvattanikā."
msgstr ""
"These seven awakening factors are creators of sight, vision, and knowledge. "
"They grow wisdom, they’re on the side of solace, and they lead to "
"extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn46.40:2.2"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.40:2.3"
msgid ""
"Satisambojjhaṅgo, bhikkhave, cakkhukaraṇo ñāṇakaraṇo paññābuddhiyo "
"avighātapakkhiyo nibbānasaṃvattaniko … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo, bhikkhave, "
"cakkhukaraṇo ñāṇakaraṇo paññābuddhiyo avighātapakkhiyo nibbānasaṃvattaniko."
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.40:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā cakkhukaraṇā ñāṇakaraṇā paññābuddhiyā "
"avighātapakkhiyā nibbānasaṃvattanikā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These seven awakening factors are creators of sight, vision, and knowledge. "
"They grow wisdom, they’re on the side of solace, and they lead to "
"extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.40:2.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.40:2.6"
msgid "Nīvaraṇavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.1"
msgid "Dve kusalā kilesā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.2"
msgid "Dve yoniso ca buddhi ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.3"
msgid "Āvaraṇā nīvaraṇā rukkhaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.4"
msgid "Nīvaraṇañca te dasāti."
msgstr ""
